.TH "skl_update_scaler_plane" 9 "skl_update_scaler_plane" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
skl_update_scaler_plane \- Stages update to scaler state for a given plane.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" skl_update_scaler_plane
.BI "(struct intel_crtc_state *crtc_state "  ","
.BI "struct intel_plane_state *plane_state "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "crtc_state" 12
crtc's scaler state
.IP "plane_state" 12
atomic plane state to update
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Return
0 - scaler_usage updated successfully
error - requested scaling cannot be supported or other error condition
